data.text: The latest issue of International Property & Travel magazine covers some of the world’s most exquisite homes for sale, beautiful holiday resorts, supercars, superyachts, watches, jewellery, fashion and high-end home decor. Art lovers will also find details of forthcoming exhibitions, auctions and fairs globally. Three award-winning interior designers share the secrets of their stunning lounge creations. We also reveal where to find the perfect Italian lakeside home and residences neighbouring one of London’s beautiful royal parks. Find out what Florida has to offer and living in Asia. Why not stay a while and experience local life as we suggest prime hotels to enjoy whilst discovering the area before purchasing a home there.
